OL,3,C'Everyone is stressed' - Residents
OL,4,Creturn to tower block months after
OL,5,Cevacuation
OL,7,FResidents of Barton House in Bristol
OL,8,Fhave described their relief and
OL,9,Ffrustration as they returned home,
OL,10,Fthree months after they were forced to
OL,11,Fleave due to safety concerns.
OL,13,FMore than 400 people - including
OL,14,Faround 100 children - their home on
OL,15,FBarton Hill on the evening of Tuesday
OL,16,F14 November.
OL,18,FFollowing an initial survey, it was
OL,19,Ffeared that structural issues could
OL,20,Fput the building at risk of collapse
OL,21,Fin the event of a fire.
