OL,3,C'Everyone is stressed' - Residents
OL,4,Creturn to tower block months after
OL,5,Cevacuation
OL,7,FDue to this, 250 people moved into
OL,8,Fhotels or with family and friends to
OL,9,Fallow additional surveys and
OL,10,Fconstruction work to be completed at
OL,11,Fthe 14-storey tower block.
OL,13,FThe fire service, engineers, and
OL,14,Fcouncil say the for residents to
OL,15,Freturn.
OL,17,FResident Jon Wisbey moved back from
OL,18,Fthe Holiday Inn on Thursday and said
OL,19,Fhe was relieved to be back after a
OL,20,F'nightmare' three months.
