OL,3,C'Everyone is stressed' - Residents
OL,4,Creturn to tower block months after
OL,5,Cevacuation
OL,7,FHe said: "It's just relief. I'm really
OL,8,Frelieved to be back, staying in the
OL,9,Fhotel was a nightmare. Everyone is
OL,10,Fstressed to the max. I feel really
OL,11,Fsorry for the people who are reluctant
OL,12,Fto come back or refusing to come back
OL,13,Fbecause they are going through hell.
OL,14,FBut personally, I'm glad to be home."
OL,16,FIt's thought up to 20 households may
OL,17,Frefuse to move back to Barton House
OL,18,Fafter the .
