OL,3,C'Everyone is stressed' - Residents
OL,4,Creturn to tower block months after
OL,5,Cevacuation
OL,7,FResident Fadumo Farah said: "We will
OL,8,Fbe staying in the hotel until we
OL,9,Ffigure out what to do next. I want the
OL,10,Fcouncil to give us another option."
OL,12,FBut Bristol City Council says it will
OL,13,Fstop paying for residents' hotels on
OL,14,FFriday, having spent more than five
OL,15,Fmillion pounds on the evacuation and
OL,16,Fsubsequent construction work.
