OL,3,C'Everyone is stressed' - Residents
OL,4,Creturn to tower block months after
OL,5,Cevacuation
OL,7,FOver the last three months, a new fire
OL,8,Falarm system has been installed and
OL,9,Fadditional fireproofing fitted.
OL,10,FIntrusive checks have also been made
OL,11,Fto ensure structural steel rods are in
OL,12,Fthe correct place.
OL,14,FThe evacuation was triggered when an
OL,15,Fexisting survey was peer-reviewed by
OL,16,Fengineers who feared the building
OL,17,Fcould be at risk of collapse if there
OL,18,Fwas a single flat fire.
