OL,3,C'Everyone is stressed' - Residents
OL,4,Creturn to tower block months after
OL,5,Cevacuation
OL,7,FBut more intrusive surveys found the
OL,8,Fstructure was, in fact, safe. Although
OL,9,Fexperts agreed fire safety work was
OL,10,Frequired before residents could move
OL,11,Fback home.
OL,13,FCouncillor Kye Dudd, Cabinet member
OL,14,Ffor Housing, Services and Energy,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We just had to act and then the
OL,16,Fmore intrusive survey showed the
OL,17,Fbuilding could be made safe and that's
OL,18,Fwhat we did. Now the fire brigade and
OL,19,Four engineers are happy that it is
OL,20,Fsafe.
