OL,3,C'Everyone is stressed' - Residents
OL,4,Creturn to tower block months after
OL,5,Cevacuation
OL,7,F"We would not wish this evacuation on
OL,8,Fanyone. But we did our best to provide
OL,9,Falternative accommodation, payments,
OL,10,Fand mental health support. Anything
OL,11,Fother than being in people's homes is
OL,12,Finferior - but we had to act with the
OL,13,Finformation we had."
OL,15,FBut tensions are still running high
OL,16,Fbetween some residents and the council
OL,17,F- who say they want somewhere
OL,18,Falternative to live after the ordeal
OL,19,Fthey have experienced.
